Text: GISB Board of Directors Meeting June GISB Board Members The GISB office apologizes for the delay in getting the meeting material out for the upcoming GISB Board meeting scheduled for June We are waiting to include some additional material regarding the Energy Industry Standards Board consideration The board book will be emailed out on Monday June and you should receive a hard copy of the material by Tuesday June If you need additional information or have any questions please call the GISB office at Best Regards GISB Office The GISB organization follows a privacy policy which does not permit distribution of contact information As such all email addresses are denoted blind in correspondence Upon receipt of notice the GISB office will modify the distribution to no longer carry your address If you would like to add other participants from your organization to this distribution list please also email such request to the GISB office
